name: Qt Install Script
summary: Learn about .QS files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: The QS file is used by the Qt creator setup program and is part of the Qt Installer Framework.
NOTE: Qt SDK was previously developed by Nokia and Digia.

description: Automation install script used by Qt, a cross-platform application development toolkit; contains data used to locate and install user-defined features; compressed with the 7zip format.
